column2: Main Pal Do Pal Ka Shayer Hoon
Tum Itna Jo Muskura Rahe Ho
Tu Nahin To Zindagi Mein Aur Kya
Tum Ko Dekha To Yeh Khayal Aaya
Yeh Tera Ghar Yeh Mera Ghar
Yeh Mera Dil Yaar Ka Deewana
Baar Baar Dekho Hazar Baar Dekho
Om Shanti Om (Meri Umar Ke Naujawano)
Unse Mili Nazar Ke Mere Hosh Ud Gai
Main Zindagi Ka Saath Nibhata Chala Gaya
Meet Na Mila Re Mann Ka
Bachna Ae Hasinon Lo Main Aa Gaya
Chura Liya Hai Tumne Jo Dil Ko
Kora Kagaz Tha Yeh Mann Mera
Chhoo Lene Do Nazuk Honthon Ko
Akele Akele Kahan Ja Rahe Ho
Khwab Ho Tum Ya Koi Haqeeqat
Are Yaar Meri Tum Bhi Ho Ghazab
Kisi Raah Mein Kisi Mod Par
Tere Chehre Mein Woh Jadoo Hai
Mere Dil Mein Aaj Kya Hai
Aaj Phir Jeene Ki Tamanna Hai
Sajna Hai Mujhe Sajna Ke Liye
Tum Aa Gaye Ho Noor Aa Gaya
Goom Hai Kisi Ke Pyar Mein
Are Jane Kaise Kab Kahan Iqrar
Tere Mere Sapne Ab Ek Rang Hain
Tere Mere Milan Ki Yeh Raina
Aaja Aaja Main Hoon Pyar Tera
Dil Tadap Tadap Ke Kah Raha
Ho Gaya Hai Tujhko To Pyar Sajna
Aajkal Paon Zameen Par Nahin Padte
Ab To Hai Tumse Har Khushi Apni
Phir Wohi Raat Hai Khwab Ki
Dekho Maine Dekha Hai Ek Sapna
Aajkal Tere Mere Pyar Ke Charche
Raat Kali Ek Khwab Mein Aai
Aao Na Gale Lag Jao Na
Chhod Do Aanchal Zamana Kya Kahega
Ye Samaa Samaa Hai Pyar Ka
Phool Tumhe Bheja Hai Khat Mein
Jo Tumko Ho Pasand Wohi Baat Karenge
Yahoo Chahe Mujhe Koi Junglee Kahen
Ye Ladka Hay Allah Kaisa Hai Deewana
Ek Hasina Thi Ek Deewana Tha
Hum Bekhudi Mein Tum Ko Pukare
Hamne Dekhi Hai Un Ankhon Ki
Kahin Door Jab Din Dhal Jaye
Ghunghroo Ki Tarah Bajta Hi Raha
Koi Jab Tumhara Hriday Tod De
Ek Din Bik Jayega Mati Ke Mol
Diye Jalte Hai Phool Khilte Hai
Chand Mera Dil Chandni Ho Tum
